    "description": {
      "value": "<p>The people of this clan are infamous for their ability to manipulate their bones in a variety of ways, known as Shikotsumyaku. Many fear them because most are known to have a love of battle that borders on bloodlust.</p><p><b>Source:</b> Mechanics/Character_Options/Occupations/Community Compendium/Kaguya Clan.md</p><p><b>Category:</b> Community Compendium</p><p><b>Prerequisite:</b> Age 8+</p><p><b>Class Skills:</b> Select 2 from Balance, Chakra Control, Climb, Intimidate, Knowledge (Ninja lore), Knowledge (Tactics), Knowledge (The Underworld), Ninjutsu, Spot, Swim, Taijutsu.</p><p><b>Feat:</b> Select one from Advanced Bloodline (Shikotsumyaku), Archaic Weapon Proficiency, Combat Martial Arts, Defensive Martial Arts, Genin, Genius Ninja, Nin Weapons Proficiency, Ninjutsu Adept, Taijutsu Adept, Toughness.</p><p><b>Reputation Bonus Increase:</b> +1</p><p><b>Affiliation:</b> You require 1 less success to learn Kaguya Hijutsu techniques.</p>"
